name: panem et circenses
description:
Janet Harlow finds herself at a run-down carnival one night with no memory of how she got there. She meets a mysterious person there, who convinces Janet to play a game. Janet does not realize the stakes of this game until it is far too late.

"Press E to talk and interact"

Contains bugs. 

ContentWarnings
  • Implied violence and gore
  • Profanity
